# Instant Pot Stuffed Bell Peppers

Based on [https://www.wellplated.com/instant-pot-stuffed-peppers/...](https://www.wellplated.com/instant-pot-stuffed-peppers) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20250801182444/https://www.wellplated.com/instant-pot-stuffed-peppers/)) and [ingredients from this Washington Post Recipe](https://www.washingtonpost.com/recipes/harissa-stuffed-bell-peppers/17096) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20220928002338/https://www.washingtonpost.com/recipes/harissa-stuffed-bell-peppers/17096))

